, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyMzIzNTEwNTUzNjE3OTI5/pat-mcgrath-labs-peel-off-mask.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEyMzIzNTEwNTUzNjE3OTI5/pat-mcgrath-labs-peel-off-mask.png 380w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEyMzIzNTEwNTUzNjE3OTI5/pat-mcgrath-labs-peel-off-mask.png 620w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyMzIzNTEwNTUzNjE3OTI5/pat-mcgrath-labs-peel-off-mask.png 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"pat mcgrath labs peel off mask\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/t_share/MjEyMzIzNTEwNTUzNjE3OTI5/pat-mcgrath-labs-peel-off-mask.png\" data-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEyMzIzNTEwNTUzNjE3OTI5/pat-mcgrath-labs-peel-off-mask.png\" height=\"1080\" width=\"1920\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhotos: Courtesy of Pat McGrath Labs; Artwork: Catie Pusateri/Fashionista\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut, the all-over sheen (accompanied by the inability to move your face) isn\u0026#39;t the only way to sport the Glass 001 Artistry Mask: McGrath also recommends a \u0026#34;spotlighting\u0026#34; technique, dabbing it solely on the high points of the face (think cheekbones, bridge of the nose and the chin) for a more wearable radiant effect. The same application process pertains to spotlighting, just dip a dampened brush into the mask and pinpoint the desired areas for an extra boost of shine.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/S522\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eTune into The Fashionista Network to join the conversation with fashion and beauty industry leaders. Sign up here.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phxbrandengagement-2\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-7\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eSubscribe to Our Newsletter\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phxlisthub-3\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-8\"\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/cs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good/MTQ1NTQ5OTY2NzI5ODE1NjA3/mtqwndi3ntcznze1oda1njgw-1.svg\" alt=\"Related Stories\"/\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cphoenix-hub data-group-size=\"4\" data-first-group-size=\"3\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cphoenix-recommendations config=\"{\u0026#34;siteDomain\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;fashionista.com\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;siteBasePath\u0026#34;:null,\u0026#34;size\u0026#34;:3,\u0026#34;widgetName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;tempest_list-hub_fashionista_article-page_title-not-found-1-1\u0026#34;}\" percentage_for_personalized_recommendation=\"50\" additional_personalized_slices=\"[]\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-recommendations\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cphoenix-recommendations config=\"{\u0026#34;siteDomain\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;fashionista.com\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;siteBasePath\u0026#34;:null,\u0026#34;size\u0026#34;:1,\u0026#34;widgetName\u0026#34;:\u00